additionalProperties.description: Key: uid of the asset. Value: action. SPAWN for shipyards, remaining for ships.

action.description: Actions taken per asset (fleet or shipyard).

actTimeout.description: Maximum runtime (seconds) to obtain an action from an agent.

agentTimeout.description: Obsolete field kept for backwards compatibility, please use observation.remainingOverageTime.

convertCost.description: The number of ships required to create a shipyard.

episodeSteps.description: Maximum number of steps in the episode.

maxRegenCellKore.description: The maximum kore over which a cell won't regenerate.

randomSeed.description: The seed used to initialize the random number generator.

regenRate.description: The rate kore regenerates on the board.

runTimeout.description: Maximum runtime (seconds) of an episode (not necessarily DONE).

size.description: The number of cells vertically and horizontally on the board.

spawnCost.description: The amount of kore to spawn a new ship.

startingKore.description: The starting amount of kore available on the board.

kore.description: Serialized list of available kore per cell on the board.

players.description: List of players and their assets.

remainingOverageTime.description: Total remaining banked time (seconds) that can be used in excess of per-step actTimeouts -- agent is disqualified with TIMEOUT status when this drops below 0.

reward.description: The amount of player owned kore (equal to players[index][0]) if the player has not been eliminated, else step_eliminated - episode_steps - 1.
